        "- Empty excerpt cards cancel as insufficient_content; do not synthesize from title-only shells.\n"
        "- Write reports to the configured channel target.\n\n"
        "## Seed Files\n"
        "- watch-list.json is the maintained watch-list seed.\n"
        f"{queue_note}"
        "- runtime/curator-config.json defines batch, report target, and runtime limits.\n",
